Eagle Aquaculture, Inc.

                    Part of Aetos Technologies, Inc., Eagle Aquaculture, Inc. is an American company located in Auburn, AL. The firm engages in catfish production and farm raising.                  




Member, Board of Directors

                    1999 - 2017                  


Cumberland Pharmaceuticals, Inc.

                    Cumberland Pharmaceuticals, Inc. engages in the acquisition, development, and commercialization of branded prescription products. Its product brands include Acetadote, Caldolor, Kristalose, Omeclamox-Pak, Vaprisol, and Ethyol. The company was founded by A. J. Kazimi on January 6, 1999 and is headquartered in Nashville, TN.                  




Non-Executive Chairman

                    Prior                  


CytoViva, Inc.

                    CytoViva, Inc. provides optical microscopy-imaging systems. Its products include hyperspectral micropscopy, enhanced darkfield micropscopy and three dimensional enhanced darkfield microscopy. The company was founded by Samuel M. Lawrence and John O. Lawrence in 2005 and is headquartered in Auburn, AL.                  





