Dr. Thomas R. Lawrence, Jr.

Lawrence,  Dr. Thomas R., Jr. Almighty God, in his divine judgment called his servant Dr. Thomas R. Lawrence, Jr. to eternal rest. "Tommy", affectionately called by family members and friends, passed on Tuesday afternoon Nov. 10, 2015 at home in hospice care. He was married to Caroline Barbosa-Lawrence for 63 years and was the farther of four children: Lisa, Dwayne, Damon and Renee and the Papa and Grandpa of four grands: Caroline, Derrick, Alyssa and Morgan. The bother of Louise Jones and Reverend James E.F. Lawrence, presiding elder retired.Funeral services will be held at Saint George's Episcopal Church on Monday, November 16th, 2015 at 12 noon in Minneapolis, Minnesota. Expression, condolences and other thoughts of kindness may be sent to: Mrs. Caroline B Lawrence, 10541 Wyoming Avenue S. Bloomington, Minnesota 55438 Telephone: 1-952-941-5368. The family request in lieu of flowers that donations be made to the Thomas R. Lawrence Scholarship Fund c/o Krimson and Kream Foundation, 5413 Nicolet Ave South, P.O. Box 138, Minneapolis, Minnesota, 55419 Please keep us in prayer
Published on November 13, 2015


